{"data":{"html":{"path":"/html/body-html-attributes","title":"Body & html attributes","content":"<h1 id=\"body--html-attributes\"><a href=\"#body--html-attributes\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Body &#x26; html attributes</h1>\n<p>Gridsome can use <a href=\"https://github.com/declandewet/vue-meta\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">vue-meta</a> to modify <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;body&gt;</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;head&gt;</code> attributes.</p>\n<h2 id=\"change-attributes-globally\"><a href=\"#change-attributes-globally\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Change attributes globally</h2>\n<p>Global body or head attributes is added in <code class=\"language-text\">src/main.js</code>.</p>\n<pre class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Vue<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> head <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Add attributes to HTML tag</span>\n  head<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>htmlAttrs <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> lang<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'en'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  \n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Add atributes to BODY tag</span>\n  head<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>bodyAttrs <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'custom-body-class'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></pre>\n<h2 id=\"change-attributes-per-page\"><a href=\"#change-attributes-per-page\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Change attributes per page</h2>\n<p>Custom attributes per page is added inside <strong>.vue components</strong>.\nFor example, <code class=\"language-text\">src/pages/About.vue</code> would look something like this:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'About'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  metaInfo<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    title<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'About us'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    htmlAttrs<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      lang<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'en'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    bodyAttrs<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'custom-body-class'</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></pre>\n","headings":[{"value":"Body & html attributes"}],"subtitles":[{"value":"Change attributes globally","anchor":"#change-attributes-globally"},{"value":"Change attributes per page","anchor":"#change-attributes-per-page"}]}},"context":{}}